---

## ‚öôÔ∏è Architecture

Sigima is organized by data type:

```text
sigima/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ tools/      # Low-level NumPy-based algorithms supporting some computation functions
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ proc/       # High-level processing functions operating on SignalObj/ImageObj
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ base/   # Common processing functions
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ signal/ # 1D signal processing
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ image/  # 2D image processing
```

Each domain provides:

- Low-level functions operating on NumPy arrays
- High-level functions operating on `SignalObj` or `ImageObj`

---

## üß™ Testing

Sigima comes with unit tests based on `pytest`.

To run all tests:

```bash
pytest
```

To run GUI-assisted validation tests (optional):

```bash
pytest --gui
```

